Package: usvn-mysql
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends} usvn-common, php5-mysql, mysql-server
Description: Graphical web interface for manage Subversion repositories. MySQL version.
   USVN is an Open Source free software which allows everyone to use Subversion in an easily way.
   It's a web tool which can manage SVN official server configuration.

