Description: Graphical web interface for manage Subversion repositories. Sqlite version.
   USVN is an Open Source free software which allows everyone to use Subversion in an easily way.
   It's a web tool which can manage SVN official server configuration.

Package: usvn-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, php5, subversion, libapache2-svn, apache2
Description: Common files for USVN.
   USVN is an Open Source free software which allows everyone to use Subversion in an easily way.
   It's a web tool which can manage SVN official server configuration.
